data.description: Spacious and Updated 2-Bedroom, 2-Bathroom Home in the Mainlands of Tamarac (Forsythe Section 16). This Community claims to be Housing for Older Persons 55+. Kitchen has been updated with newer Cabinets, Stainless Steel Appliances and Countertop. Split Bedroom Floorplan with Flex/Den area. Open Living/Dining Room. Tiled Throughout! X-Large Enclosed Patio plus Pavered Open Patio out back. 1-Car Garage and 2-Car Driveway. Lush Landscaping. Full-Sized Washer / Dryer. Garage Door has been Upgraded. BRAND NEW Flat Roof in Progress. Great Homeowners Association with Clubhouse and Pool plus Many Activities. Low HOA fee of $95 includes lawn care, roof power washing yearly and painting exterior of the home every 5 years. Roof Replaced 2001. AC 2011.
